data.description: Nestled in the charming community of Pinnacle Ridge, 396 Scrub Oaks Dr is a true gem that beckons you to experience its many delights. From the moment you arrive, the meticulously manicured landscaping and inviting front porch set the tone for the extraordinary curb appeal this home offers. As you step inside, the foyer graciously ushers you into the heart of this residence, promising a warm and welcoming atmosphere.The living room boasts a gas fireplace that calls for cozy evenings and warm gatherings, seamlessly connected to the open kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, elegant granite countertops, and a convenient breakfast peninsula for quick bites. A spacious pantry is a culinary hideaway, and the adjacent dining area leads to a covered porch where you can enjoy meals while overlooking the expansive fenced-in backyard.The main floor hosts a spacious master suite, complete with a trey ceiling, walk-in closet, dual vanity, garden tub, and a separate shower. Two additional bedrooms share a stylish full bathroom on the main floor, and a separate laundry room adds to the convenience of daily life. Upstairs, a fourth bedroom, a full bathroom, and a versatile family bonus room await.Beyond the doorstep, you'll find a wealth of nearby attractions, including the ICWW, numerous golf courses, Topsail Island, and the captivating Wrightsville beaches. The location is also convenient to shopping centers, top-notch schools, and the vibrant city of Wilmington, home to a prestigious university and a thriving business network in its historic river district.Luxurious touches abound, with brand-new oak wide plank luxury laminate  flooring throughout the entire house and a fresh coat of paint. Bathrooms and light fixtures have been tastefully updated to modern standards.As a cherry on top, this property offers incredible bonus features, including a whole house generator hookup, RV hookup, garden shed, and a treehous treehouse playset, ensuring that everything you need for a well-rounded and comfortable lifestyle is right at your fingertips.
